      *
      * Access SAR Details to determine if ERZ237 is switched ON
     C                     MOVE 'N'       ERZ237  1
      *
     C                     CALL 'AOSARDR0'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   RTCD
     C                     PARM '*VERIFY' OPTN
     C                     PARM 'ERZ237'  SARD
     C           SCSARD    PARM SCSARD    DSFDY
      *
      ** If feature is switched ON, set a variable field to
      ** condition the rest of the processing
      *
     C           RTCD      IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ERZ237
     C           CFT156    IFNE 'Y'
     C                     OPEN OTPAY
     C                     OPEN INPAY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
